data.description: Elegance and tranquility await in this gorgeous 2/2 Ernie White home in 55+ Lake James! Once you step inside you will see the craftsmanship from the upgraded lighting, crown molding and tray ceilings, to the high quality tile floor that graces most of the living space. A gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space and tile backsplash start off the open floor plan, which also includes as breakfast nook, great room, and access to the tranquil screened lanai, making family gatherings or entertaining a breeze. The en suite sits separate from the other bedroom, and features a generous bedroom and stunning bathroom. The bathroom hosts a large walk in closet, dual sinks, 2 separate linen closets, and beautiful walk in shower. Both showers feature tile walls. Garage has epoxy floors and ample space for 2 cars, and serene backyard has a paver extended area perfect for grilling! Close to shopping, restaurants and more, but tucked away and quiet, get the best of both worlds!
